data.description: This well maintained 4 bedroom 3 full bath home has an inviting front porch an open floor plan. The details in the home will be noticed from the moment you walk in the front door. A beautiful gas log fireplace is flanked with built in bookcases on both sides. The kitchen island is great for gathering around for entertaining. The screened porch is just off of the kitchen/dining space. The master bedroom. And 2nd bedroom are downstairs. Upstairs your find a open loft area, a full bathroom and 2 more generous sized bedrooms.  The community offers a beautiful community swimming pool and walking trail around the lake.
